carts.name: FORMAT 300 mL. DIESEL FUEL ADDITIVE
carts.description:
DIESEL FUEL ADDITIVE Specially formulated for turbo and diesel vehicles, this diesel fuel additive is produced using nano-technology. It effectively cleans the entire system, from the fuel tank to the combustion chamber, preventing rust and corrosion. By increasing the cetane number in the molecular structure of diesel fuel, it maximizes fuel efficiency, resulting in significant fuel savings through highly efficient complete combustion. This advanced diesel fuel technology also prevents freezing and enhances the flow of fuel. By absorbing water and moisture in the fuel, it ensures improved diesel fuel combustion. In new-generation diesel and turbo vehicles, it delivers superior performance and reliability, ultimately translating into cost savings.
300 ml x 24 Ad./Pcs.

carts.name: FORMAT 200 mL. GUN LUBRICATE & MAINTENANCE
carts.description:
The gun lubrication spray not only performs the lubrication process, but also extends the periodic maintenance period. In addition, it takes on a role of preventing the formation of rust by blocking the effects of moisture and water. It is assured that there are no raw materials in its contents that could potentially damage the ammunition capsule. This product is a spray that combines Decontamination, lubrication and protection functions.
200 ml x 24 Ad./Pcs.
